@startuml
!include theme.iuml
title Payment Saga — Orchestration and Compensation States
[*] --> PAYMENT_PENDING : reservation pending\nidempotency key accepted
PAYMENT_PENDING --> RECONCILING : gateway timeout / unknown
PAYMENT_PENDING --> PAYMENT_SUCCEEDED : gateway confirms capture
PAYMENT_PENDING --> PAYMENT_FAILED : definitive decline
RECONCILING --> PAYMENT_SUCCEEDED : status query = captured
RECONCILING --> PAYMENT_FAILED : status query = declined
RECONCILING --> PAYMENT_TIMEOUT : reservation TTL / retry budget exhausted
PAYMENT_SUCCEEDED : confirm reservation\nbook seats\nissue tickets\npublish events
PAYMENT_FAILED : cancel reservation\nrelease locks\npublish failure
PAYMENT_TIMEOUT : expire reservation\nrelease locks\nflag late-callback reconciliation
PAYMENT_SUCCEEDED --> [*]
PAYMENT_FAILED --> [*]
PAYMENT_TIMEOUT --> [*]
note right of RECONCILING
  Never compensate an uncertain payment immediately.
  Query by provider idempotency/reference first to avoid
  charging a customer after their seats were released.
end note
@enduml
